- `design_token_escape`: replaces raw inline literals like `#ff00aa`, `#0a0a0a`, `#cccccc`, `#1a73e8`, `rgb(...)`, and pixel spacing with Tailwind/token-backed classes such as `bg-surface`, `text-ink`, `border-brand`, `p-6`, and `shadow-sm`. This aligns with the fixture’s `tailwind.config.ts` token source.

- `responsive_fragility`: replaces fixed `width: 800`, `width: 720`, and fixed pixel font sizing with `w-full max-w-3xl`, responsive grid columns, `min-w-0`, and text scale classes. The card can now shrink on small screens and switch from one column to two columns at `sm`.

